<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<ContentPage xmlns="http://xamarin.com/schemas/2014/forms"
             xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml"
             x:Class="MatematicaBacMD.Views.Combinatorica"
             xmlns:ffimageloading="clr-namespace:FFImageLoading.Forms;assembly=FFImageLoading.Forms"
             Style="{StaticResource background}">
    <ContentPage.Content>
        <ScrollView>
            <StackLayout Padding="15">
                <Label Text="Combinatorica" Style="{StaticResource TitleLable}"/>
                <BoxView HeightRequest="2" BackgroundColor="White"/>
                <Label Style="{StaticResource Info}" Margin="0,25,0,10">
                    <Label.FormattedText>
                        <FormattedString>
                            <Span Style="{StaticResource Important}" Text="Combinatorica "/>
                            <Span Style="{StaticResource Information}">este ramur&#259; matematicii care se ocup&#259; cu studiul mul&#539;imilor (de obicei finite) de obiecte &#351;i modalit&#259;&#539;ile de a le combina, asocia sau pune laolalt&#259;.</Span>
                        </FormattedString>
                    </Label.FormattedText>
                </Label>
                <BoxView HeightRequest="1" BackgroundColor="White"/>
                <Label Style="{StaticResource Info}" Margin="0,20,0,10">
                    <Label.FormattedText>
                        <FormattedString>
                            <Span Style="{StaticResource Important}" Text="Combin&#259;rile&#10;&#10;"/>
                            <Span Style="{StaticResource Information}" Text="Combin&#259;rile se refer&#259; la combinarea de n lucruri luate c&#226;te k odat&#259; f&#259;r&#259; a se repeta.&#10;
De exemplu, fiind date trei fructe (un m&#259;r, o portocal&#259; &#351;i o par&#259;), exist&#259; trei combin&#259;ri a c&#226;te dou&#259; fructe care pot fi extrase din acest set:&#10;- un m&#259;r &#351;i o par&#259;&#10;- un m&#259;r &#351;i o portocal&#259;&#10;- o par&#259; &#351;i o portocal&#259;"/>
                        </FormattedString>
                    </Label.FormattedText>
                </Label>
                <ffimageloading:CachedImage
                        WidthRequest="250"
                        HeightRequest="60"
                        HorizontalOptions="Center" 
                        VerticalOptions="Center"
                    Source="i2.jpg">
                </ffimageloading:CachedImage>
                <Label Style="{StaticResource Info}" Margin="0,20,0,10">
                    <Label.FormattedText>
                        <FormattedString>
                            <Span Style="{StaticResource Information}" Text="De exemplu, putem calcula num&#259;rul combin&#259;rilor posibilie pentru alc&#259;tuirea unei m&#226;ini de 5 c&#259;r&#539;i dintr-un pachet standard de 52:"/>
                        </FormattedString>
                    </Label.FormattedText>
                </Label>
                <ffimageloading:CachedImage
                        WidthRequest="400"
                        HeightRequest="60"
                        HorizontalOptions="Center" 
                        VerticalOptions="Center"
                    Source="i3.jpg">
                </ffimageloading:CachedImage>
                <Label Style="{StaticResource Info}" Margin="0,20,0,10">
                    <Label.FormattedText>
                        <FormattedString>
                            <Span Style="{StaticResource Information}" Text="Totodat&#259;, putem folosi formula combin&#259;rilor utiliz&#226;nd factorialii &#351;i simplifica factorii de la num&#259;r&#259;tor cu o parte din factorii de la numitor, dup&#259; care va r&#259;m&#226;ne de efectuat doar &#238;nmul&#539;irea factorilor r&#259;ma&#351;i:"/>
                        </FormattedString>
                    </Label.FormattedText>
                </Label>
                <ffimageloading:CachedImage
                        WidthRequest="500"
                        HeightRequest="318"
                        HorizontalOptions="Center" 
                        VerticalOptions="Center"
                    Source="i4.jpg">
                </ffimageloading:CachedImage>
                <BoxView HeightRequest="1" BackgroundColor="White"/>
                <Label Style="{StaticResource Info}" Margin="0,20,0,10">
                    <Label.FormattedText>
                        <FormattedString>
                            <Span Style="{StaticResource Important}" Text="Aranjamentele&#10;&#10;"/>
                            <Span Style="{StaticResource Information}" Text="&#206;n practic&#259;, de multe ori se ajunge la necesitatea de a alege dintr-o mul&#539;ime oarecare de obiecte submul&#539;imi care au anumite propriet&#259;&#539;i sau de a aranja elementele unei mul&#539;imi &#238;ntr-o numit&#259; ordine.&#10;&#10;
Defini&#539;ie: Dac&#259; A este o mul&#539;ime cu n elemente, atunci submul&#539;imile ordonate ale lui A, av&#226;nd fiecare c&#226;te k elemente, unde 0 &#8804; k &#8804; n, se numesc aranjamente de n elemente luate c&#226;te k.&#10;&#10;"/>
                        </FormattedString>
                    </Label.FormattedText>
                </Label>
                <ffimageloading:CachedImage
                        WidthRequest="250"
                        HeightRequest="60"
                        HorizontalOptions="Center" 
                        VerticalOptions="Center"
                    Source="i5.jpg">
                </ffimageloading:CachedImage>
                <Label Style="{StaticResource Info}" Margin="0,20,0,10">
                    <Label.FormattedText>
                        <FormattedString>
                            <Span Style="{StaticResource Important}" Text="Propriet&#259;&#539;i&#10;&#10;"/>
                        </FormattedString>
                    </Label.FormattedText>
                </Label>
                <ffimageloading:CachedImage
                        WidthRequest="276"
                        HeightRequest="130"
                        HorizontalOptions="Center" 
                        VerticalOptions="Center"
                    Source="i6.jpg">
                </ffimageloading:CachedImage>
                <BoxView HeightRequest="1" BackgroundColor="White"/>
                <Label Style="{StaticResource Info}" Margin="0,20,0,10">
                    <Label.FormattedText>
                        <FormattedString>
                            <Span Style="{StaticResource Important}" Text="Permut&#259;rile&#10;&#10;"/>
                            <Span Style="{StaticResource Information}" Text="Permutarea este un concept matematic care se refer&#259; &#238;n mod uzual la num&#259;rul de
posibilit&#259;&#539;i de rearanjare a unei liste ordonate de valori sau obiecte.&#10; 
Cel mai simplu exemplu de permutare este dat de c&#259;tre o anagram&#259; - de exemplu, 
literele cuv&#226;ntului CARTE (toate distincte &#238;ntre ele) pot fi rearanjate form&#238;nd cuv&#226;ntul TRACE sau ECART.&#10;&#10;
Num&#259;rul de permut&#259;ri ale unei mul&#539;imi de elemente este dat de produsul numerelor (de ordine ale elementelor) 
de la 1 la n, cunoscut ca n! (n factorial)"/>
                        </FormattedString>
                    </Label.FormattedText>
                </Label>
                <ffimageloading:CachedImage
                        WidthRequest="178"
                        HeightRequest="58"
                        HorizontalOptions="Center" 
                        VerticalOptions="Center"
                    Source="i7.jpg">
                </ffimageloading:CachedImage>
            </StackLayout>

        </ScrollView>
    </ContentPage.Content>

</ContentPage>